16:10.470 --> 16:14.600
Doggy.

16:18.728 --> 16:20.856
Feet hurt.

16:21.022 --> 16:22.945
Thwack!

16:25.485 --> 16:26.953
They're all wet!

16:27.111 --> 16:29.034
Thwack!

16:29.197 --> 16:31.541
Stop this.
My feet, Mum.

16:31.699 --> 16:33.542
MY feet!

16:33.701 --> 16:35.829
My feet are burning!

16:35.995 --> 16:37.542
You have to stop
this now!

16:37.705 --> 16:38.831
Wait. My hands!

16:38.998 --> 16:39.794
Wait. Wait.

16:39.957 --> 16:40.833
Thwack!

16:41.000 --> 16:42.092
Liam?

16:42.251 --> 16:43.127
Liam, what happened?

16:43.294 --> 16:44.637
My hands!

16:46.631 --> 16:48.008
My hands!

16:48.174 --> 16:50.393
I put my hands inside the man!

16:59.143 --> 17:01.111
Uh, let me out!

17:01.270 --> 17:02.066
Margaret?
Let me out!

17:02.230 --> 17:03.152
Enough.
Let me out.

17:03.314 --> 17:04.406
Uh, let me out!

17:04.565 --> 17:05.691
All right, put him back.

17:05.858 --> 17:07.280
Let me out!
Let me out!

17:07.443 --> 17:08.444
- Mum!
- What's happening?

17:08.611 --> 17:10.329
Do something.
My feet are burning!

17:10.488 --> 17:12.707
What's happening?!
Let me out!

17:12.865 --> 17:15.993
Help! Let me! Please. For God's
sake, get him out of there!

17:16.160 --> 17:17.752
Let me out!

17:17.912 --> 17:19.914
My feet are burning!

17:20.080 --> 17:20.957
They're burning.

17:21.123 --> 17:24.002
Let me out!

17:24.167 --> 17:27.342
Let me out!
Let me out!

17:27.505 --> 17:29.007
Let me out.

17:34.387 --> 17:36.640
He's stable.

17:36.806 --> 17:38.023
It's all right, sweetie.

17:39.475 --> 17:42.479
I'm here.

17:42.645 --> 17:45.899
I'm here.

17:46.065 --> 17:48.568
<i>I'm here.</i>

17:51.445 --> 17:53.914
How can she ever...

17:54.073 --> 17:56.326
