17:56.492 --> 17:58.244
She can't.

17:58.411 --> 18:00.709
Charlie must have...

18:03.291 --> 18:06.170
He must have brought him in
from the cold, and then...

18:10.089 --> 18:12.387
Poor Charlie.

18:48.085 --> 18:49.712
Dad?

18:49.879 --> 18:51.552
What?

18:52.923 --> 18:54.766
I'm very tired.

18:54.925 --> 18:57.019
I know... pet.

18:57.178 --> 18:58.930
Here. Come here.
Give me a hand.

19:00.765 --> 19:03.564
I can't get me big fat fingers
in here. Look.

19:05.144 --> 19:06.771
Look.

19:06.937 --> 19:08.439
You see these?
See these two wires?

19:08.606 --> 19:10.199
Uh-huh. The black
and the red one.

19:10.358 --> 19:12.611
Yup. I want you to touch
them together for me.

19:12.777 --> 19:14.324
Why?

19:14.487 --> 19:16.535
'Cause it'll make the
engine start. Come on.

19:16.697 --> 19:18.119
Can't you do it?

19:18.282 --> 19:19.750
No. I can't, pet.

19:19.909 --> 19:22.128
Because you've hurt your hand?

19:22.286 --> 19:24.084
No. I haven't.

19:24.246 --> 19:26.715
You have. I know you have. Carrie,
will you do as I tell you?

19:26.874 --> 19:28.501
Touch the two wires
together, please.

19:28.668 --> 19:30.011
No.
Carrie!

19:30.169 --> 19:32.968
No! You'll do as
you're fucking told!

19:33.130 --> 19:36.600
Do as you're fucking told,
touch the wires together,

19:36.759 --> 19:39.228
