of here. Please.

19:39.387 --> 19:42.937
No,Dad, I
don't want to anymore.

19:43.099 --> 19:46.649
I want to go home.

19:46.811 --> 19:49.234
I want to go back to school.

19:49.397 --> 19:52.401
I want to see Liam.

19:52.566 --> 19:54.989
I'm only ten, Dad.

19:55.152 --> 19:56.950
I'm only ten.

19:57.113 --> 19:58.660
